# Override default ergonomic heap (was -Xms16045m -Xmx16045m, ~50% of 31G RAM).
# Lowered to 4G on 2026-05-11 to free memory for OCF / RS business processes.
# Rationale: this ES instance only indexes RS metadata + small text corpora; 4G is comfortable.
# To restore: delete this file, restart elasticsearch.
-Xms4g
-Xmx4g
EOF
sudo chown elasticsearch:elasticsearch /opt/elasticsearch/config/jvm.options.d/heap.options
sudo chmod 660 /opt/elasticsearch/config/jvm.options.d/heap.options
sudo systemctl restart elasticsearch
```

ES 1 秒起来（索引仅 2.6mb）。

#### B) 16G swap

```bash
