### 27.3 数据库

```sql
CREATE TABLE ai_series_ocf_progress (
  id INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  task_id INT NOT NULL,
  project_ref INT NOT NULL,
  episode_index INT NOT NULL,
  kind VARCHAR(32) NOT NULL,
    -- stage_start | stage_design | stage_prompt
    -- char_photo     key='陈一一|基础'
    -- scene_panel    key='巷子|格1'
    -- shot           key='P01'
    -- artifact       key='director|storyboard|character_lib|scene_lib'
  key_str VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL DEFAULT '',
  status ENUM('done','failed') NOT NULL,
  resource_ref INT NULL,
  err TEXT NULL,
  ts DATETIME DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
  UNIQUE KEY u_task_progress (task_id, kind, key_str),
  KEY k_lookup (project_ref, episode_index, kind, key_str, status)
);
```

- **UNIQUE (task_id, kind, key_str)**: 同 task 内同 kind+key 不重复(`ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE` 兜底)
- **KEY (project_ref, episode_index, kind, key_str, status)**: 跨 task 复用查找(忽略 task_id)

